name: Untitled 25042021 (I)
description: @DolCreative - #HENThousand. Created using spray paint, acrylic paint, posca pens, and pintasa markers. Blending together pop art, street art, and neo-expressionism to a vibrant conclusion. Brighter colours than my typical work, but, as always a reflection on mental health. Here the vibrancy, and reduced materials compared to other pieces, reflect clarity of thought, focus, and positivity in current artistic endeavours. 600 DPI digital image (PNG) of original A4 piece.
